name: Pendant necklace in rustic hunter green woven silk thread with a solid core and resin and mother of
description:
The core of this necklace is a beautiful dark rustic hunter green, and it features lighter green and brown accents to add visual appeal. Hanging down from the necklace is a small loop with a silk cord and attached to this is a stunning resin and mother of pearl shell chip pendant. Subtle glitter highlight effects just like sunlight on water, that catch the light.

Measurements: Diameter 9mm, 20 Inch Strand
Color: Army green, hunter green and chocolate brown silk
Material: Silk, Jade, Mother of Pearl and Embedding Resin
Pendant: Mother of Pearl chips resin donut pendant measures just under 3" (7cm)

name: Feather headband in cinnamon satin embellished with red and green pheasant feathers and spiral of sa
description:
Rich harvest autumn tones in a lovely spicy dark cinnamon colored hand stitched satin covered headband with rich red and woodland green oval pheasant feather pad. Also highlighting this headband is a 3mm wide old gold satin ribbon snail shell spiral with a white freshwater pearl heart. This headband is suitable and comfortable for all headsizes from small to large.

Measurements:
Feather pad measures 5" (12.5cm) long by 4" (10cm) wide.
